artnerships scholarships and mentorships entrepreneurship etc reducing the gap between skillset and market demands “we are a family business driven by the values of respect excellence and entrepreneurial spirit we believe that sustainability is the balance between economic priorities promoting empowerment for all stakeholders and environmental protection this year we are celebrating  years of building brands in the region and throughout our journey we have learned and we are convinced thatpress releasesustainable business is in an opportunity to create value while making the world a better place” said patrick chalhoub coceo of the chalhoub group environmental conservation is also a key issue addressed through the un global compact and as a member the chalhoub group is expected to follow high standards of responsibility the last half decade has seen unprecedented economic growth for the region but with this has come an increased demand for energy and natural resources the chalhoub group strives to reduce the environmental footprint through engagement awareness and efficiency of operations “our commitment to environmental sustainability continues to be driven by the engagement of our stakeholders through an education and awareness process several of the gcc countries contribute to the highest rate of greenhouse gas emissions per capita and fall within the scope of our regional operations the key challenge is turning this trend around is a change of mindset we are obliged as a business operation in these countries to advocate for environmental protection” said anthony chalhoub coceo of the chalhoub group as part of their commitment and through this membership the chalhoub group has promised to release an annual report sharing their sustainability performance this report has received third party verification from the global reporting initiative a leading organisation in this field promoting this way of reporting for organisations to become more concerned about the future the group has embarked on this journey of sustainability knowing the path is long and with many obstacles along the way   about the chalhoub group the chalhoub group is the leading partner for luxury across the middle east since  as an expert in retail distribution and marketing services based in dubai the group has become a major player in the beauty fashion and gift sectors regionally by blending its middle east expertise and intimate knowledge of luxury the chalhoub group is building brands in the region by offering service excellence to all its partners and a unique experience to its customers through its passionate teams with a growing workforce of more than  people implemented in  countries as well as operating over  retail stores the groups success is attributed to its most valued asset highly skilled and dedicated teams professionalism and passion are what fuel the chalhoub groups competitive edge in todays market by being committed to implementing sustainable practices into their business the chalhoub group was awarded in  for the second consecutive year the csr label from the dubai chamber of commerce and has been accepted as a new member of the united nations global compact community for more information please visit wwwchalhoubgroupcom or contact rachel el helou  events  pr specialist    rachelelheloumailmacnet next previous press kit sign in press kit this section is exclusively reserved for journalists if you wish to know more about the chalhoub group please login or create a user account to access this section the press kit is available in english french arabic and italian   download   chalhoub group legal notice privacy notice  how it all began an untapped market for international highend brands a couple passionate about france’s culture and its savoirfaire decided to open the first christofle boutique in damascus this is how michel chalhoub and his wife widad transformed their passion into a business that showcased their confidence in the middle east’s development giving birth to what is now known as the chalhoub group  damascus michel and widad chalhoub open the first christofle boutique in damascus syria marking the beginning of the chalhoub group activities   delegation birth of “delegation” for regional brand representation in the middle east    beirut move of the chalhoub family and activities to beirut    kuwait first local partnership with ali habchi in kuwait    regional distribution start of the regional distribution of beauty fashion  gifts in kuwait    kuwait chalhoub activities moved to kuwait anthony chalhoub anthony chalhoub joins the chalhoub group    advertising initiation of advertising activities in kuwait    patrick chalhoub patrick chalhoub joins the chalhoub group    tanagra birth of “tanagra” a timeless luxury concept store in kuwait the preferred destination for stylesavvy globalists to find the quintessence of elegance curated by experts with a finger on the luxury pulse   louis vuitton opening in kuwait of the first louis vuitton boutique in the middle east region  faces opening of the first “faces” beauty concept store now known as wojooh offering a sophisticated fusion of luxury unconventional niche and specialty brands as well as expert advice to fulfil every need of the beauty savvy  dubai invasion of kuwait triggered the move of some of the chalhoub group’s activities to dubai uae kingdom of saudi arabia appointment of radwa trading company limited as distributor in the kingdom of saudi arabia    kuwait airport duty free management of kuwait airport duty free by habchi  chalhoub wll    bahrain incorporation of ashraf bgdc for perfumes and cosmetics wll for local distribution  retail in bahrain    puig joint venture with puig a thirdgeneration familyowned fashion and fragrance business based in barcelona  dubai takeover of the management of allied enterprises llc a dubai based retail and distribution company cairo incorporation of mac company for promoting commercial business wll for local distribution  retail in egypt  euro rscg joint venture between promopub limited and havas sa previously euro rscg    saks fifth avenue introducing saks fifth avenue american luxury department store chain coty joint venture with coty global beauty products manufacturer founded in paris by françois coty fendi joint venture with fendi cairo airport duty free management of cairo airport duty free  dior joint ventures with french luxury goods companies christian dior couture and parfums christian dior sephora joint venture with sephora french chain of cosmetics stores founded in paris qatar incorporation of qatar luxury company wll for local distribution  retail in qatar  chalhoub retail academy launch of the chalhoub retail academy delivering an internationally recognised education programme and ensuring excellent customer service for the various stores  havas group regional collaboration with havas group one of the largest global advertising and communications groups in the world  opening of over  shops opening of over  shops making the chalhoub group one of the key retailers in the middle east region in the beauty fashion and gifts sectors  chalhoub impact creation of chalhoub impact the sustainable engagement strategy of the chalhoub group    christian louboutin joint venture with christian louboutin french footwear designer brand    katakeet opening of the first “katakeet” in abu dhabi a unique luxury children’s wear concept store conceived around storytelling ensuring a unique retail experience for both parents and children  level shoe district opening of “level shoe district” now known as level shoes in dubai mall the world’s finest shoe metropolis targeting the luxury consumer through its unparalleled collection of exclusive footwear and bespoke services  tdesign tanagra opens “tdesign” in dubai a meeting space for luxury design lovers featuring a showroom for bespoke limited editions luxury design and custommade pieces  wow by wojooh launch of “wow by wojooh” the first makeup line inspired by the middle east consumer dedicated to and exclusively for oriental beauty which combines the chalhoub group’s deep understanding of the region and its knowledge of the beauty sector  tryano opening of “tryano” in yas mall abu dhabi a specialty store dedicated to beauty bags and children offering a oneofakind experience with over  of the worlds most soughtafter international and local brands      level kids opening of level kids in city walk dubai a concept store dedicated to children’s luxury offering a comprehensive selection of childrenswear shoes accessories toys and specialised services under one roof    contact us inquiry type please select general inquiry corporate pr business development full name email subject message thank you for submitting your enquiry we will get back to you as soon as possible if you are interested in joining us please apply through our careers website chalhoubgroupcareerscom legal notice legal notice this legal notice describes the conditions of use of our websites wwwchalhoubgroupcom and chalhoubgroupcareerscom the “website” by connecting to the website you acknowledge that you have read understood and accepted without limitation or reservation these conditions of use and undertake to respect them the website is owned and operated by mct fze a jebel ali free zone establishment organized and existing under the laws of the emirate of dubai under the trading licence  domiciled at po box  jebel ali dubai –united arab emirates tel        “chalhoub” chief editors  mariehélène strauss and angelica d’andlau content chalhoub commits itself to ensuring to the best of its ability that the information posted on the website is correct and uptodate chalhoub reserves the right to correct the websites content at any time and without notice however chalhoub cannot guarantee the correctness precision thoroughness or completeness of the information available on the website availability you acknowledge that i it